welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Parkville, a charming city known for its beautiful parks and friendly atmosphere. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer during your stay. Enjoy your time in Parkville!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport is a small, single-story building with limited amenities.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at BWI airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at BWI airport is primarily used by Southwest Airlines for domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at BWI airport serves domestic flights for various airlines, including American Airlines and Delta.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at BWI airport serves domestic and international flights for multiple airlines, including JetBlue and Spirit.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Tipton AAF Airport is exclusively for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lee Airport serves all commercial flights and includes a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lee Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.
